HEADWORD: Dynamization
<hw>Dy"na*mi*za`tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <ety>[Gr. <?/ power. See
<er>Dynamic</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Homeop.)</fld> <def>The act of setting
